# QuickDecide — Groq API keys
#
# You can provide MULTIPLE keys for 24-hour rotation + automatic failover.
# The app alternates the primary key every 24h and, on timeout/rate-limit,
# transparently falls over to the next key.
#
# Option A — individual variables (recommended, easiest on Vercel):
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your_first_key_here
GROQ_API_KEY_2=gsk_your_second_key_here
# ...up to GROQ_API_KEY_20
#
# Option B — one comma-separated variable (handy for local dev):
# GROQ_API_KEYS=gsk_key1,gsk_key2,gsk_key3
#
# A single GROQ_API_KEY alone still works fine (no rotation, no failover).
